&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-rubrics&#34;&gt;What is Rubrics?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rubrics is a Shiny web application for assessment with rubrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The application allows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create a rubric for an exam or test.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load the list of students from a csv file and generate a template for the assessment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load the assessment from the template.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate a list with the students grades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate a descriptive summary of the distribution of grades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate a personalized report with the assessment of each student.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
